applecore.cfg.show.saturation.hud.overlay.tooltip=§7If true, shows your current saturation level overlayed on the hunger bar
applecore.cfg.show.food.values.hud.overlay.tooltip=§7If true, shows the hunger (and saturation if "Show Saturation HUD Overlay" is true) that would be restored by food you are currently holding
applecore.cfg.show.food.exhaustion.hud.underlay.tooltip=§7If true, shows your food exhaustion as a progress bar behind the hunger bars
applecore.cfg.show.food.stats.in.debug.overlay.tooltip=§7If true, adds a line that shows your hunger, saturation, and exhaustion level in the F3 debug overlay
